description: Best practices for using Tailwind CSS for styling
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,css}
---
- Use utility-first approach for consistent and maintainable styles, but create custom components for reusability
- Implement responsive design using Tailwind's responsive modifiers
- Create custom themes and extend Tailwind's default configuration
- Use `@apply` directive to create component-specific styles
- Utilize responsive design utilities for mobile-first development
- Keep your tailwind.config.ts organized and maintainable
